8x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Queens-Of-The-Stone-Age">Queens Of The Stone Age</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Bicep">Bicep</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Justin-Timberlake">Justin Timberlake</a>等已被宣布为<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/electric-castle">Electric Castle</a> 2025 的第一批表演者。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/photos/music-photos/story-electric-castle-festival-2019-pictures-gallery-2531423">2019 年罗马尼亚电动城堡节的图片故事</a></strong></li></ul><p>一年一度的音乐盛典将回到特兰西瓦尼亚班菲城堡内的克卢日纳波卡音乐节举办地。据新闻稿称，音乐节承诺从 7 月 16 日到 20 日，为期五天的 24 小时不间断的音乐和魔术表演。</p><p>其他将在音乐节上表演的乐队包括<a href="/artists/Justice">Justice</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Refused">Refused</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Leprous">Leprous</a> 、 <a href="/artists/The-Amazons">The Amazons</a> 、 <a href="/artists/The-Sisters-of-Mercy">The Sisters of Mercy</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Nilüfer-Yanya">Nilüfer Yanya</a> 、 Joey Valence &amp; Brae 、 <a href="/artists/Sofi-Tukker">Sofi Tukker 、</a> <a href="/artists/Shaggy">Shaggy</a>等。</p><p>粉丝们可以<a href="http://electriccastle.ro/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买音乐节的门票。门票起价为 159 欧元（130 英镑），另加费用。 EC 村还提供露营住宿，每晚 15 欧元（12 英镑）起。查看下面的完整节日阵容。 </p><figure id="attachment_3821359" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3821359" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3821359" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Electric-Castle-2025-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="电动城堡 2025 年阵容海报。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2500" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Electric-Castle-2025-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Electric-Castle-2025-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Electric-Castle-2025-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Electric-Castle-2025-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Electric-Castle-2025-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Electric-Castle-2025-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3821359" class="wp-caption-text">电动城堡 2025 年阵容海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>除了现场音乐之外，新闻稿还承诺，参加者还可以在节日期间“探索城堡里的时尚市场、乘坐热气球、在露营地上蹦极、在篮球场和排球场上观看比赛，这是最受欢迎的白天时间”喜剧俱乐部和 EC 讲座、烧烤野餐以及在湖畔森林中的轻松时光。”</p><p>今年的 Electric Castle 吸引了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/massive-attack">Massive Attack</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">Bring Me The Horizo​​n、</a> Queens Of The Stone Age、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chase-and-status">Chase &amp; Status</a> (live)、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/khruangbin">Khruangbin</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sleaford-mods">Sleaford Mods</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bonobo">Bonobo</a> (DJ set)、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nina-kraviz">Nina Kraviz</a> 、Eats Everything、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jayda-g">Jayda G</a>等乐队等等。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《石器时代女王》讲述如何克服困难、与戴夫·格罗尔的“浪漫”以及接下来的发展" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qBq0-baxRAc?start=534&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他新闻中，Queens Of The Stone Age 的主唱<a href="/artists/Josh-Homme">Josh Homme</a>最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mark-lanegan-60-london-tribute-gig-roundhouse-josh-homme-dave-gahan-chrissie-hynde-footage-photos-setlist-watch-3819599">在伦敦 Roundhouse 举办的一场众星云集的演出中表演，向已故的 Mark Lanegan 致敬</a>。</p><p>在其他地方，贾斯汀·汀布莱克<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-cancels-oklahoma-city-show-due-to-back-injury-3817517">最近因背部受伤取消了在俄克拉荷马城的演出。</a></p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/queens-of-the-stone-age-bicep-justin-timberlake-lead-electric-castle-2025-line-up-in-transylvania-3821357">石器时代女王、Bicep 和 Justin Timberlake 领衔特兰西瓦尼亚 2025 年电动城堡阵容</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
